articles.title: Bank of America profit rises 10% - Yahoo Finance
articles.description: The second-largest US bank got a boost from higher interest income and a strong performance from its Wall Street unit.
articles.content:
Third quarter profits at Bank of America (BAC) were up 10% from a year ago, as the second-largest US bank got a boost from higher interest income and a strong performance from its Wall Street unit.
